{"tid":845094,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[環保撚］食鹽含塑膠微粒","createTime":"2018-10-02T11:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T11:48:50.000Z","uid":169992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e3a1234f1d4f93207b0834233cee91736c5e3060","tid":845094,"uid":169992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:29:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jTScfIzipe8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjTScfIzipe8&d=6dggj3QqVcJ%2F2O%2By4evOwMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=5d168cd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jTScfIzipe8</a><br />\n<br />\n海洋裡的塑膠垃圾經過裂解後，成為小於5毫米的「塑膠微粒」，去年各國陸續發表海鹽遭到汙染。清大研究團隊這回針對台灣的食鹽研究，果然在裡頭發現片狀、條狀和顆粒狀塑膠微粒，數量難以估計。雖然還沒有研究證實塑膠微粒對人體有危害，不過有專家提出，它很容易沾黏有害物質，可能引起部分癌症、過動症等疾病。 <br />\n<br />\n清大教授凌永健說，「它（塑膠微粒）已經從環境進入到食物鏈，那進入到食物鏈，最後的受體就是人」，凌永健指出「目前是沒有證據去證明說它對人體有危害，但是也沒人敢說它是沒有危害。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=436668\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D436668&d=6dggj3QqVcJ%2F2O%2By4evOwMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=81862603\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D436668&h=b72bc31e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=436668</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n塑化調會影響人類生殖系統，影響精子品質、男嬰女性化、增加患<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睪丸</span>癌、乳癌等疾病風險"},{"pid":"bee0d5ac895c7eac8b5803e441a51d4a11ed5b8e","tid":845094,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}